<h1 id="markdowntemplate">MarkdownTemplate</h1>
<p>Turns comments into markdown.</p>
<a name='renderComments'>
<h2>
renderComments</a>
</h2>

<pre><code>renderComments(self, comments)
</code></pre>
<p>Renders a bunch of comments as markdown.</p>

